{"tid":1389804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登發言人：強烈譴責韋柏非法集結 破壞社會安寧","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:22:46.000Z","uid":2617,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16f8e5d9f06b712a11075e0b4811b719373d9966","tid":1389804,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"昨天自下午開始韋柏在南海進行未經批准的集結，其中在北部一帶有激進對流作出挑戰國家主權行為，包括增強、向北移動，甚至以載有烈風風力的雨帶推向香港防線，對香港要上班的市民構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n熱帶風暴韋帕目無法紀，以風力破壞社會安寧，阻住市民搵食，我們予以強烈譴責，會繼續全力支持天文台嚴正執法，遏止所有北移行為，盡快改發三號風球，回復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月31日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間11時50分"},{"pid":"6d0ea7a5380bafad1208fc2bcbae076b1e206f67","tid":1389804,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83c2ab46cbaf4e792435d1b08f7fc9203177f8d","tid":1389804,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下一齊呼籲罷工 幫手推<br />\n<br />\n有人為你衝，你肯唔肯為佢唔返工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8a5fc68e83c3a51020ab6a341d537e9d85b2f48","tid":1389804,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83c2ab46cbaf4e792435d1b08f7fc9203177f8d","tid":1389804,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下一齊呼籲罷工 幫手推<br />\n<br />\n有人為你衝，你肯唔肯為佢唔返工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d439b3594cd2b1d5f248612992f5ba13e33bd026","tid":1389804,"uid":39205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a5fc68e83c3a51020ab6a341d537e9d85b2f48","tid":1389804,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"